        <title>Radioactive Molecules as Laboratories of Fundamental Physics</title>
            <categories>physics.atom-ph hep-ex nucl-ex</categories>
            <comments>Published in $\textit{Nature Reviews Physics}$ (2026), see http://www.nature.com/articles/s42254-026-00950-9 . 28 pages, 5 figures</comments>
